name: Why do women kill
description: But sooner or later, awareness comes. When adrenaline and shock fade away, even the bloodiest killers are short-circuited. Our heroine was desperate and reckless, so she committed the crime in a fit of madness, and then she realized the horror of what she had done... And with the realization came the madness, because there is no way back, the work is done and now her hands are forever in blood.
